I"i#<p>The following resources describe initiatives that helped individuals with disabilities transition from educational settings to competitive, integrated employment.</p>

<p><a href="https://employmentfirstma.org/pages/pp.html"><strong>Promising Practices for Transition from School to Work</strong></a></p>

<p>This webpage provides resources and lessons learned from the implementation of various initiatives serving transition-age youth in Massachusetts on their path to employment.</p>

